    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to share this absolute gem with you! Honestly, it's in such incredible shape, it still feels brand new. I've babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly maintained. If you\u2019re looking for something that looks and drives perfectly, this is the one! You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
