      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s been tucked away in a garage since day one. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
