      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-level E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing replacement, addressing all critical preventative maintenance. The ZF 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with tactile precision, sending power through a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with zero bushing play, ensuring the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. Every seal is bone-dry, and the undercarriage reflects a life of climate-controlled storage.",
